How is a user-defined exception raised?

```sql
DECLARE
  e_low EXCEPTION;
  v_bal NUMBER := 50;
BEGIN
  IF v_bal < 100 THEN
    ______ e_low;
  END IF;
EXCEPTION
  WHEN e_low THEN
    DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE('too low');
END;
```
